      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "## AI CI/CD pipeline\n\nThis board tracks **application HTTP metrics** scraped from `/metrics` (Express + `prom-client`). Wire **GitHub Actions** and **OpenAI** run history in the app dashboard at **`/ai-dashboard`** on port 3000.\n\n**Jobs:** AI code review · AI test ideas · Failure insights · Log anomaly check · Optional auto-fix PR.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (route) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_count[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HTTP request rate by route",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
